description: Agave: Marmorata | A very special specimen, the tepeztate is a wild maguey that offers various benefits such as food, ornament, medicine and of course mezcal, but is in serious danger of disappearing. [ Peligro ] An interpretation of breathing, is part of the audiovisual NFT pieces of the series “Memorias Orgánicas” a work of exploration and registration through 3D scanning on endemic natural elements of Oaxaca, Mexico. | 1080 x 1080 px | http://f3.studio/ | IG: @f3.output TW: @F3_STUDI0
